{"tid":605711,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"成晚冇瞓直接去左返學","createTime":"2018-03-26T02:04:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-27T17:38:05.000Z","uid":23758,"like":40,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"0f70c8560668315a433b4d7e52a5698ecc7cadb0","tid":605711,"uid":23758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T02:04:15.000Z","msg":"個身熱熱地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 完全唔眼訓又唔係好攰<br />\n係張床碌左成晚訓唔到又諗左好多野<br />\n雖然訓唔到又攤左成晚係咪可以當有訓過<br />\n沖涼又繼續諗野，諗到遲到都唔覺<br />\n唔知幾時會突然暴斃死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢個世界係得自己先信得過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n對人打開心都係弱智行為<br />\n冇人會care你，就好似你都唔應該care任何人一樣"},{"pid":"cfc1d5cdf450d32791556647c3da2986cb0e7dfe","tid":605711,"uid":8867,"like":4,"dislike":31,"score":-27,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T02:06:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"42493304df8c1acc6a783416e7acd73610c6808d","tid":605711,"uid":39706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T02:06:56.000Z","msg":"如果自已都愛唔自已, 人哋又點樣愛你呢?"},{"pid":"5bb9604cf0874ce5ffa47a9117d254e56d84280d","tid":605711,"uid":23758,"like":27,"dislike":6,"score":21,"quote":{"pid":"cfc1d5cdf450d32791556647c3da2986cb0e7dfe","tid":605711,"uid":8867,"like":4,"dislike":31,"score":-27,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T02:06:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T02:12:53.000Z","msg":"右你老母<br />\n有人唔做走去做狗"},{"pid":"61ea91ea0324fde2efa85a9fd963c81b0689175b","tid":605711,"uid":23758,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"42493304df8c1acc6a783416e7acd73610c6808d","tid":605711,"uid":39706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T02:06:56.000Z","msg":"如果自已都愛唔自已, 人哋又點樣愛你呢?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T02:14:23.000Z","msg":"愛自己先要同人群隔離<br />\n唔洗再比人煩到，開開心心做自己鍾意既野<br />\n都唔洗比人傷害"},{"pid":"0efeda088ad36797f94c0e1db66c35070b78d63f","tid":605711,"uid":97439,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedB